From Syed Zaeem Hosain Subject Re Acceleration sensor In article Michael DeAddio writes Does anyone know of any type of acceleration sensor that has an electrical output of any sort It would only have to sense acceleration in one Thanx Mike I am not sure about this but I believe that Analog Devices in Norwood MA makes a relatively inexpensive acceleration sensor primarily for use in auto air bag systems I do not know specs or anything else but you might give them a call to find out more Z Syed Zaeem Hosain Box Z Consulting Group San Jose CA